    <h1>Understanding the Car Price Data</h1>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Data Overview</h2>
        <div class="subsection">
            <p><strong>Dataset:</strong> CarPrice_Assignment.csv</p>
            <p><strong>Context:</strong> US market car data collected for Geely Auto's market entry analysis</p>
            <div class="highlight">
                Primary objective: Understand pricing dynamics for car design and business strategy development
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. Data Analysis Steps</h2>
        
        <h3>Data Cleaning Process</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Missing value identification and handling</li>
            <li>Outlier detection and treatment</li>
            <li>Data consistency verification</li>
            <li>Data type validation</li>
        </ul>

           <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Variable Relationships</h2>
        <table class="correlation-table">
            <tr>
                <th>Variable</th>
                <th>Correlation with Price</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Horsepower</td>
                <td>0.81 (Strong Positive)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Curb Weight</td>
                <td>0.87 (Very Strong Positive)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Engine Size</td>
                <td>0.87 (Very Strong Positive)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Fuel Efficiency</td>
                <td>-0.68 to -0.70 (Strong Negative)</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Initial Insights</h2>
        <div class="highlight">
            <h3>Key Findings:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Strong positive correlation between price and performance metrics (horsepower, engine size)</li>
                <li>Vehicle weight shows strongest correlation with price</li>
                <li>Inverse relationship between fuel efficiency and price</li>
                <li>Car dimensions show moderate to strong influence on pricing</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
